data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER WELCOMES YOU HOME!! This beautiful property boasts 1.6 acres of country living in a cul de sac with the option to add your very own gorgeous pool or shop in highly sought afte Windy Hill Estates with NO HOA! This home offers an open concept 3 bedroom, 2 and a half bath with an office floor plan. Granite countertops, laminate and tile flooring throughout, dedicated dinning room, updated HVAC system, updated hot water heater, newer stove top and dishwasher and a gorgeous view overlooking your spacious back yard and a deck to enjoy those evening sunsets. This beautiful home really has it all!
